{"tid":803481,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"克羅地亞教練炮轟C.朗拿度：他很自私 只在乎自己入球","createTime":"2018-09-02T10:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T09:39:22.000Z","uid":20634,"like":123,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7057fe31b2bd5f84121c5ab8ac184a31f94f7a","tid":803481,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/09/02/2/218c69a94dd8c2c1a65d90ea460de70f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F2%2F218c69a94dd8c2c1a65d90ea460de70f.jpg&h=f6257e02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　近日，克羅地亞教練達里奇接受Sportske Novosti採訪時，炮轟C.朗拿度，認為C.朗拿度是一名自私的球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　達里奇說：「C.朗拿度很自私，我永遠不希望他出現在我的球隊里。他就是這類球員，他會這麼想，&lsquo;即使我們輸波了，我以為在乎的事情就是我有沒有入球&rsquo;。」<br />\n<br />\n　　此前結束的歐洲足協頒獎典禮，C.朗拿度沒有參加，他的前隊友莫迪歷獲得歐洲足協賽季最佳球員。而C.朗拿度的姐姐以及經理人文迪斯，都公開炮轟，為C.朗拿度不滿。"},{"pid":"793780901a25796040882ac235e58b57f5bd4353","tid":803481,"uid":43117,"like":1,"dislike":40,"score":-39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"關自私事？"},{"pid":"7dc305efb5992845ecd7d63434c24756b57f7b4d","tid":803481,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00173d1870bd120228db8af01b68d0d9d397949a","tid":803481,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a715de6b7513384795aa3db30bdde0101587f3e8","tid":803481,"uid":25831,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aff69e34026df5a8ed275a308630eff898d2cb85","tid":803481,"uid":120852,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"賤種全面失蹤"},{"pid":"86381ea1681e090b34d437d1055cdadcb6d1ad71","tid":803481,"uid":187719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T1